Install Postfix/Dovecot with Vpopmail interface to the MySQL backend
   1. curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/qmtoaster/posttoasty/main/install.sh --output /usr/local/bin/posttoasty
   2. chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/posttoasty
   3. posttoasty
   4. Features: https://www.linuxbabe.com/mail-server/setup-basic-postfix-mail-sever-ubuntu
